---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Despre AXA IT"
  description="AXA IT — peste 10 ani experiență, 150+ sisteme în 7 industrii. Misiunea noastră: să facem tehnologia să lucreze pentru tine. Parteneri TP-Link, Fortinet, Ubiquiti, Microsoft."
>
  <Header variant="light" currentPage="/despre" />

  <main class="bg-brand-light min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-28 pb-16 md:pb-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-brand-light overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-24 left-1/4 w-[320px] h-[320px] bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[90px] pointer-events-none" />
      <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-full mb-6">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.09 9.09 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-brand-blue text-[13px] font-medium">Cine suntem</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-[32px] md:text-[44px] font-bold text-brand-dark tracking-tight leading-tight">Despre AXA IT</h1>
          <p class="mt-5 text-brand-steel text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-relaxed">
            Suntem echipa din spatele infrastructurii IT a zeci de companii din România: <strong class="text-brand-dark">soluții complete</strong>, de la mentenanță și rețele la cloud și securitate — cu focus pe rezultate măsurabile, nu pe promisiuni goale.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About / Mission -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white border-y border-brand-border/40">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-[26px] md:text-[32px] font-bold text-brand-dark mb-6">Experiență și încredere</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-[16px] leading-relaxed mb-4">
              De <strong class="text-slate-800">peste 10 ani</strong> construim și menținem sisteme IT pentru business-uri care nu își permit downtime-ul: rețele stabile, backup-uri verificate, securitate la zi și suport când contează.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
              Am implementat și monitorizat <strong class="text-slate-800">peste 150 de sisteme</strong> în <strong class="text-slate-800">7 industrii</strong> diferite — de la producție și logistică la retail și servicii profesionale.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-brand-accent/10 rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-60" />
            <blockquote class="relative bg-brand-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 text-white shadow-xl shadow-brand-dark/10">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-accent/80 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-[18px] md:text-[20px] font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/95">
                Misiunea noastră — <span class="text-brand-accent">să facem tehnologia să lucreze pentru tine</span>.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-6 text-white/50 text-[14px] leading-relaxed">
                Ne asumăm partea tehnică ca să te poți concentra pe creșterea afacerii: infrastructură predictibilă, costuri clare și un partener care răspunde.
              </p>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-14">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-full mb-5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-brand-blue text-[13px] font-medium">Valorile noastre</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] font-bold text-brand-dark">Ce ne diferențiază</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-brand-steel text-[16px] max-w-xl mx-auto">Principii după care lucrăm zi de zi cu clienții noștri.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-border/60 hover:border-brand-accent hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-100/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-dark font-semibold text-[18px] mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Rapiditate</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-steel text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Intervenții și răspunsuri în timp util — pentru că IT-ul tău nu așteaptă.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-border/60 hover:border-brand-accent hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-100/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.594 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h2.593c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.213 1.281c.063.374.313.686.645.87.074.04.147.083.22.127.324.196.72.257 1.075.124l1.217-.456a1.125 1.125 0 011.37.49l1.296 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01-.26 1.431l-1.003.827c-.293.24-.438.613-.431.992a6.759 6.759 0 010 .255c-.007.378.138.75.43.99l1.005.828c.424.35.534.954.26 1.43l-1.298 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.369.491l-1.217-.456c-.355-.133-.75-.072-1.076.124a6.57 6.57 0 01-.22.128c-.331.183-.581.495-.644.869l-.213 1.28c-.09.543-.56.941-1.11.941h-2.594c-.55 0-1.02-.398-1.11-.94l-.213-1.281c-.062-.374-.312-.686-.644-.87a6.52 6.52 0 01-.22-.127c-.325-.196-.72-.257-1.076-.124l-1.217.456a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.369-.49l-1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01.26-1.431l1.004-.827c.292-.24.437-.613.43-.992a6.932 6.932 0 010-.255c.007-.378-.138-.75-.43-.99l-1.004-.828a1.125 1.125 0 01-.26-1.43l1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 011.37-.491l1.216.456c.356.133.751.072 1.076-.124.072-.044.146-.087.22-.128.332-.183.582-.495.644-.869l.214-1.281z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-dark font-semibold text-[18px] mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Personalizare</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-steel text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Soluții adaptate dimensiunii și domeniului tău — fără pachete „universal" care nu se potrivesc.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-border/60 hover:border-brand-accent hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-100/50 transition-all duration-300 group sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-dark font-semibold text-[18px] mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Top Partners</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-steel text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Lucrăm cu branduri recunoscute în industrie pentru echipamente și licențe de încredere.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-border/60 hover:border-brand-accent hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-100/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-dark font-semibold text-[18px] mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Durabilitate</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-steel text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Arhitectură și mentenanță gândite pe termen lung, nu doar „reparații rapide".</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-border/60 hover:border-brand-accent hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-100/50 transition-all duration-300 group sm:col-span-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-dark font-semibold text-[18px] mb-2 group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Suport 24/7</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-steel text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Monitorizare și linii de intervenție pentru incidente critice — disponibilitatea ta contează la fel de mult ca a noastră.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-brand-dark text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]" />
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-brand-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[100px]" />
      </div>
      <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-10">
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.07] transition-colors">
            <p class="text-brand-accent font-bold text-[36px] md:text-[44px] tracking-tight">150+</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-[15px] mt-1">sisteme</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.07] transition-colors">
            <p class="text-brand-accent font-bold text-[36px] md:text-[44px] tracking-tight">10</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-[15px] mt-1">ani experiență</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.07] transition-colors">
            <p class="text-brand-accent font-bold text-[36px] md:text-[44px] tracking-tight">7</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-[15px] mt-1">industrii</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.07] transition-colors">
            <p class="text-brand-accent font-bold text-[36px] md:text-[44px] tracking-tight">24/7</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-[15px] mt-1">monitorizare &amp; suport critic</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partners -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-[28px] md:text-[36px] font-bold text-brand-dark">Parteneri tehnologici</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-brand-steel text-[16px] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Colaborăm cu lideri globali în echipamente de rețea, securitate, wireless și software enterprise.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
          {['TP-Link', 'Fortinet', 'Ubiquiti', 'Microsoft'].map((name) => (
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-[100px] px-6 py-8 rounded-2xl border border-brand-border/60 bg-brand-light/80 hover:border-brand-accent hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-100/40 transition-all duration-300">
              <span class="text-slate-800 font-semibold text-[18px] tracking-tight">{name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-blue/10 border border-brand-blue/20">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
            <div>
              <p class="text-brand-blue text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Partener principal securitate</p>
              <p class="text-brand-dark font-bold text-[20px]">Consal Security</p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-[15px] mt-2">Certificare <span class="font-medium text-slate-800">ARTS</span> — soluții de securitate fizică și integrare aliniate la standarde înalte.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-xl border border-blue-100 text-brand-blue text-[13px] font-medium shadow-sm">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
                </svg>
                ARTS certified
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-brand-light border-t border-brand-border/40">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-[26px] md:text-[32px] font-bold text-brand-dark">Hai să vorbim despre proiectul tău</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-brand-steel text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
          Contactează-ne pentru o consultație — analizăm nevoile tale și îți propunem un plan clar, fără obligații.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-brand-blue hover:bg-brand-blue/90 text-white font-semibold text-[16px] px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/25"
        >
          Mergi la Contact
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
